generic_domain: Domain: multivariate time series from a complex operational system. System: multiple interacting components equipped with sensors and actuators, operating under coordinated control logic. Signals: heterogeneous sensor measurements capturing system states, exhibiting cross-variable correlations and varying noise levels. Dynamics: non-stationary temporal behaviors with mode switching, long-range dependencies, and occasional distributional shifts. Anomalies: abnormal patterns caused by component faults, control deviations, or unexpected state transitions that disrupt normal system coordination.
